    <measure>Association Between Screening Methods (Meibomian Gland Expression) and Treatment Effectiveness Outcomes (Total Meibomian Gland Score)</measure>
    <time_frame>Baseline and 4 Weeks</time_frame>
    <description>Analysis of association between Baseline Meibomian Gland Expression Score and Total Meibomian Gland Score at 4 Weeks. Success was defined by demonstration of a statistically significant (p&lt;0.05) association between the screening method and outcome.
